title: Silent Witnesses
description: In this Dateline classic, when a young woman is found dead in a field on the outskirts of Green Bay, Wisconsin, a Fitbit helps detectives solve the mystery. Andrea Canning reports. Originally aired on NBC on May 11, 2018.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
